metadata.description:
THIS IS THE OFFICIAL RELEASE OF THE FR3NZ EP! 

LAST YEAR I WENT CRAZY WITH COLLABS WITH WHO I CONSIDER TO BE THE MOST TALENTED ARTISTS IN WEB3!

1. DUBAI WAY W/ LUCA MAXIIM & MoRuf (PROD. LUCA MAXIIM)
2. SOUL TALK W/ SIIMBIIE LAKEW (PROD. ALLAN KINGDOM)
3. SUNBURNT W/ JAMEE CORNELIA (PROD. JAMEE CORNELIA)
4. PRIORITIES (PROD. GRL)

BESIDES MY BROTHER SIIMBIIE I MET ALL OF THESE AMAZING ARTISTS VIA WEB3, SELLING MUSIC NFTS, AND ON TWITTER SPACES. 

ALL OF THESE SONGS HAVE INDIVIDUALLY SUCCESSFULLY BEEN SOLD AS MUSIC NFTS. 

THE EP IS ON ALL STREAMING PLATFORMS 4/20. 

MY NEXT ALBUM DROPPING SOON. MUCH LOVE, YEBO!
